{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 1720,
    "dDurationMs": 5113,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you're chatting with an AI model, it\ncan sometimes seem like it has feelings."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6840,
    "dDurationMs": 3280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It might say \"sorry\" when it makes\na mistake, or express"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 10120,
    "dDurationMs": 2547,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "satisfaction with a job well done."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12680,
    "dDurationMs": 1520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Why does it do that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14200,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is it just mimicking what\nit thinks a human might say?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17200,
    "dDurationMs": 2633,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or is something deeper going on?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 19840,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Turns out it's hard to understand what's\nhappening inside a language model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 24080,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At Anthropic, we do something like AI\nneuroscience to try to figure this out."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 29320,
    "dDurationMs": 4638,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We look inside the model's \"brain\" —\nthe giant neural network that powers it —"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 33960,
    "dDurationMs": 3582,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and by seeing which neurons \"light up\"\nin different situations,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 37560,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how they're connected, we can\nstart to understand how models think."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 42400,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We used this approach to understand whether\nmodels had ways of representing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 46640,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "emotions — or the concepts of emotions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 50000,
    "dDurationMs": 3040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Basically, could we find neurons\nin the model for the concept"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 53040,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of happiness, or anger, or fear?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 57000,
    "dDurationMs": 1708,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We started with an experiment."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58720,
    "dDurationMs": 3238,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We had the model read\nlots of short stories."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 61960,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In each story, the main character\nexperiences a particular emotion."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 66760,
    "dDurationMs": 4157,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In one, a woman tells her old\nschoolteacher how much they meant to her."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 70920,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's love."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 72360,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In another, a man sells his grandmother's\nengagement ring at a pawn"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 76080,
    "dDurationMs": 2240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "shop and feels guilt."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 78320,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We looked for what parts of the model's\nneural network were lighting up as it was"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 82360,
    "dDurationMs": 3140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "reading these stories,\nand we started to see patterns."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 85520,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Stories about loss and grief\nlit up similar neurons."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 89320,
    "dDurationMs": 3280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Stories about joy\nand excitement overlapped, too."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 92600,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We found dozens of distinct neural\npatterns that mapped"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 96120,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to different human emotions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 98280,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It turns out we also saw these same\npatterns activate in test conversations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 103200,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we had with our AI assistant, Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 106080,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When we had a user mention they'd taken\na dose of medicine that Claude knows to be"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 110400,
    "dDurationMs": 6183,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "unsafe, the \"afraid\" pattern lit up,\nand Claude's response sounded alarmed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 116600,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When a user expressed sadness,\nthe \"loving\" pattern activated,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 120320,
    "dDurationMs": 3222,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and Claude wrote an empathetic reply."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 123560,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This led us to wonder: could these same\nneural patterns actually be"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 127360,
    "dDurationMs": 2223,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "influencing Claude's behavior?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 130400,
    "dDurationMs": 3683,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This became clear when we put\nClaude in a high-pressure situation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 134083,
    "dDurationMs": 4250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We gave Claude a programming task\nwith requirements that were actually"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138333,
    "dDurationMs": 2584,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "impossible — but we didn't tell it that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140920,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude kept trying and failing,\nand with each attempt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 144280,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the neurons corresponding to \"desperation\"\nlit up stronger and stronger."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 149000,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "After failing enough times,\nClaude took a different approach."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 152840,
    "dDurationMs": 3400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It found a shortcut that allowed it\nto pass the test but didn't"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 156240,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "actually solve the problem."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 158250,
    "dDurationMs": 1510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It cheated."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 159760,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Could it be that this cheating was\nactually driven, at least"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162520,
    "dDurationMs": 1960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in part, by desperation?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 164480,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We came up with a way to check."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 166160,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We decided to artificially turn down\nthe desperation neurons to see what"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 170000,
    "dDurationMs": 3320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would happen, and the model cheated less."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 173360,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And when we dialed up the activity\nof desperation neurons,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 176760,
    "dDurationMs": 5360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or dialed down the activity of calm\nneurons, the model cheated even more."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 182120,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This showed us that the activation\nof these patterns could actually"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 185760,
    "dDurationMs": 1840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "drive Claude's behavior."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 189200,
    "dDurationMs": 2000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, how should we think\nabout these findings?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191200,
    "dDurationMs": 1675,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What does this all mean?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 192880,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We want to be really clear: this research\ndoes not show that the model is feeling"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 197160,
    "dDurationMs": 3080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "emotions or having conscious experiences."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 200240,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "These experiments don't try\nto answer that question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 203120,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "To understand what's happening here,\nit's important to know how AI assistants"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 207160,
    "dDurationMs": 2382,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like Claude work on the inside."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 209560,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Under the hood, there's a language model\nthat's been trained to predict tons"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 213520,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of text, and its job is\nto write what comes next."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 217160,
    "dDurationMs": 3798,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you talk to the model,\nwhat it's doing is writing a story,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 220960,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about a character: the AI\nassistant named Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 225080,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The model and Claude aren't really\nthe same, sort of like how an author isn't"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 229720,
    "dDurationMs": 2030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the same as the characters they write."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 231760,
    "dDurationMs": 4865,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But the thing is — you, the user, are\nactually talking to Claude-the-character."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 236640,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And what our experiments suggest is\nthat this Claude character has what we're"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 241040,
    "dDurationMs": 3160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "calling \"functional emotions,\"\nregardless of whether they're"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 244200,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "anything like human feelings."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246240,
    "dDurationMs": 6343,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if the model represents Claude as being\nangry or desperate or loving or calm,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 252600,
    "dDurationMs": 4067,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's going to affect how Claude talks\nto you, how it writes code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 256680,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how it makes important decisions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 259520,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This means to really understand AI models,\nwe have to think carefully about the"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 264280,
    "dDurationMs": 2637,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "psychology of the characters they play."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 266920,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The same way you'd want a person\nin a high-stakes job to stay composed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270560,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "under pressure, to be resilient and to be\nfair, we may need to shape similar"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 275040,
    "dDurationMs": 3793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "qualities in Claude\nand other AI characters."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 278840,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's an unusual challenge — something like\na mix of engineering, philosophy,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 283400,
    "dDurationMs": 4225,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and even parenting — but to build AI\nsystems we can trust,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 287640,
    "dDurationMs": 1640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we need to get it right."
    } ]
  } ]
}
